      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA ENVY (8) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at his last five runs. Last start finished 2nd on June 7 over 350m at Healesville behind Cumulate beaten a neck (19.31) in a Mix 6/7. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from three starts. Expected to feature in the finish again. ASTON MACHINE (6) charged out of the boxes with a strong early split and went straight to the front, scoring an all the way win (29.90) over 525m at The Meadows. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. CREATING (1) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 7 lengths into second (29.90) at this track in a Mix 6/7 over 515m. Can measure up. BRAVE ISLAND (4) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.",
